message.text:
[Groovers ‘25-‘26: TamHunt 2025 – Operating Board Application Guidelines]

𝗝𝗢𝗜𝗡 𝗧𝗛𝗘 𝗦𝗨𝗣𝗣𝗢𝗥𝗧 𝗨𝗡𝗜𝗧! 🛡️

The backbone of every mission is a strong support team—and this is your call to action! Here are the guidelines for non-performing member applications.

🗓️ 𝗔𝗽𝗽𝗹𝗶𝗰𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗣𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗼𝗱: September 10–16, 2025 (FORM CLOSES AT 11:59 PM)
👤 𝗧𝗮𝗿𝗴𝗲𝘁 𝗔𝘂𝗱𝗶𝗲𝗻𝗰𝗲: Open to All FEU–ITHM Students
🔗 𝗔𝗽𝗽𝗹𝗶𝗰𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗟𝗶𝗻𝗸: https://bit.ly/ITHMGrooversMembershipApplications2025

📌 Step up, bring your strategy, and help assemble a winning team. May your application hit the mark! 🎯

Pubmat By:
Hisami Muramatsu
Ian Canlas
Micaella Alegiojo

Caption By: Mae Saeed

#TamHunt2025 
#MembershipApplications2025
#AfterGround
#ITHMGroovers

message.text:
Dear Aspiring IABF Student Leaders,

Akala mo ba pag sports ay puro laro lang? 

hindi lang 'yon.

I remember my first year as part of the Sports Division’s executive committee. While helping organize the sportsfest, I also had the chance to represent IABF in the FEU Athletic League, with the full support of the division.

Apart from that, they helped shape my leadership skills, not just in the sport I love, but also as a student leader with one goal: to serve the IABF community.

I couldn’t believe we were able to create such happy memories just by serving our fellow IABF students. Kaya, ikaw! Yes, ikaw! 🫵 if you are into sports and want to expand your leadership skills while playing the sport you love, this division is for you!

cc: Jade Ann Ilagan Jillian Franchezka Dayao

message.text:
Dear Aspiring IABF Student Leaders,

Akala mo ba pag sports ay puro laro lang? 

hindi lang 'yon.

I remember my first year as part of the Sports Division’s executive committee. While helping organize the sportsfest, I also had the chance to represent IABF in the FEU Athletic League, with the full support of the division.

Apart from that, they helped shape my leadership skills, not just in the sport I love, but also as a student leader with one goal: to serve the IABF community.

I couldn’t believe we were able to create such happy memories just by serving our fellow IABF students. Kaya, ikaw! Yes, ikaw! 🫵 if you are into sports and want to expand your leadership skills while playing the sport you love, this division is for you!

cc: Jade Ann Ilagan Jillian Franchezka Dayao

message.text:
Dear Aspiring IABF Student Leaders,

Akala mo ba pag sports ay puro laro lang? 

hindi lang 'yon.

I remember my first year as part of the Sports Division’s executive committee. While helping organize the sportsfest, I also had the chance to represent IABF in the FEU Athletic League, with the full support of the division.

Apart from that, they helped shape my leadership skills, not just in the sport I love, but also as a student leader with one goal: to serve the IABF community.

I couldn’t believe we were able to create such happy memories just by serving our fellow IABF students. Kaya, ikaw! Yes, ikaw! 🫵 if you are into sports and want to expand your leadership skills while playing the sport you love, this division is for you!

cc: Jade Ann Ilagan Jillian Franchezka Dayao

message.text:
Dear Aspiring IABF Student Leaders,

Akala mo ba pag sports ay puro laro lang? 

hindi lang 'yon.

I remember my first year as part of the Sports Division’s executive committee. While helping organize the sportsfest, I also had the chance to represent IABF in the FEU Athletic League, with the full support of the division.

Apart from that, they helped shape my leadership skills, not just in the sport I love, but also as a student leader with one goal: to serve the IABF community.

I couldn’t believe we were able to create such happy memories just by serving our fellow IABF students. Kaya, ikaw! Yes, ikaw! 🫵 if you are into sports and want to expand your leadership skills while playing the sport you love, this division is for you!

cc: Jade Ann Ilagan Jillian Franchezka Dayao
